'''[[Middle East]]ern [[Hip hop music|hip hop]]''' is hip hop music and culture originating in the Middle East.  It is performed in many languages such as [[English language|English]], local [[Arabic]] dialects, [[Hebrew]], [[Persian language|Persian]], and [[French language|French]]. It is highly influenced by [[American hip hop]].

